<br>
This is not to say I dislike EQ... I don't.  But I either never play a MMORPG again, or I find something that accepts being able to play 10 hours a week and not be relegated to the same kind of boredom EQ would require with that little time committment.<br>
<br>
The lack of high end content is hardly troubling to me... as that is part of the problem with EQ now... the committment required in order to accomplish higher end content.<br>
<br>
As far as not liking PvP... it just needs to be implemented well.  Not being able to communicate with the enemy is a big part of me enjoying the pvp, actually-- I will happily lose my ability to give and receive &quot;nice fight&quot; tells if I don't ever have to deal with &quot;U suck HAHAHAHAHHA I ganked yu fuk0r!&quot;<br>
<br>
Pvp systems also allow you to play for a very short time, find someone to play against... and then log out.  Much like logging into Yahoo games, playing a game of chess, and logging out.<br>
<br>
Variety is the spice of life. <p><center>    <b>Aktar Mythmaker <b></center></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=6796.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=6830.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=6705.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=6705.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6705.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6705.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out of Mana<option valu